{"tid":1680353,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"高等法院(修訂)針對警員及家屬「起底」臨時禁制令","createTime":"2019-10-28T18:14:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T23:00:21.000Z","uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"79a5b73d3aa91676266b73460181d09d4e4e522a","tid":1680353,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T18:14:53.000Z","msg":"<strong>針對有警員及家屬被「起底」，律政司司長和警務處處長早前向法庭申請單方面禁制令，高等法院昨日就臨時禁制令，作出修訂。<br />\n<br />\n就有關禁制沒有相關人士同意下使用、發佈、傳達或披露屬於警務人員、配偶或家庭成員的個人資料，加入前提是「同時有意圖或相當可能會恐嚇、騷擾、威脅、煩擾或干擾相關人士的情況下」。<br />\n<br />\n禁制發佈的資料，包括但不限於他們的姓名、職位、住宅地址、辦公地址、學校地址、電子郵件地址、出生日期、電話號碼、香港身份證號碼或其他任何官方身份證明文件的號碼、Facebook帳戶ID、Instagram帳戶ID、車牌號碼和警務人員、配偶或家庭成員的任何照片。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其餘禁制事項不變，包括禁制任何人非法及故意地恐嚇、騷擾、威脅、煩擾或干擾任何警務人員、配偶或家庭成員，即父母、子女或兄弟姊妹。<br />\n</strong><br />\n臨時禁制令有效至下月8日上午10時30分。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1488717-20191029.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1488717-20191029.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=SKXI%2FGePWbtdtN3kaacFP%2Fkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=2895fdf1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1488717-20191029.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=818f4dee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1488717-20191029.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"370d4d477c7797b65f4871a27d895aef57df4da2","tid":1680353,"uid":220701,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T18:16:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除咗hkid 其他都得？"},{"pid":"804691d668b5f0d5d78efc51ab8a528583b5984b","tid":1680353,"uid":147367,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T18:19:31.000Z","msg":"根本李漢民既講法，我哋任何做法都唔會令到佢哋驚，所以唔中前提"},{"pid":"8c0047a673e04ea7a567484bc8e0bfae6d5e0441","tid":1680353,"uid":136893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T18:20:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">記唔記得7、8月既時候，臨有行動前一日既連登，係充滿住遊行路線、離開方法、行動目的地既街坊整既攻略、仲有各種各樣既行動資訊整合，所有行動都係至小早半個月搞，有D 活動更加係會根據其重要性去調配，例如我記得葵青區遊行係推遲左成個月的。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n睇下啦，2、3樓都仲有資訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />記得睇下<br />\n<br />\n【正視聽：反思行動及行動數量】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1680287\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1680287</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"05cc13e1f3acedb93930d918e08ba46e45969ab1","tid":1680353,"uid":43173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T18:24:24.000Z","msg":"表揚算唔算？"},{"pid":"148fb7437eb415dcd3bfe76ac7f41f4829203693","tid":1680353,"uid":311238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T18:27:11.000Z","msg":"救人呀！！有手足想自殺<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1680356\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1680356</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6a9a99f624581c08d607f2dc681badc7ebe66675","tid":1680353,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T22:40:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"839c15adc428f1c2732c23f33964adc50c8547a3","tid":1680353,"uid":65449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T23:00:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">記唔記得7、8月既時候，臨有行動前一日既連登，係充滿住遊行路線、離開方法、行動目的地既街坊整既攻略、仲有各種各樣既行動資訊整合，所有行動都係至小早半個月搞，有D 活動更加係會根據其重要性去調配，例如我記得葵青區遊行係推遲左成個月的。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n睇下啦，2、3樓都仲有資訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />記得睇下<br />\n<br />\n【正視聽：反思行動及行動數量】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1680287\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1680287</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}